### Build-a-Bank · Step 1 · hello-service
### Use with VS Code "REST Client", IntelliJ HTTP Client, or copy the curl equivalents below.
### Start the app first:  make run-hello   (or  .\mvnw.cmd -pl services/hello spring-boot:run )

@host = http://localhost:8080

### Your first endpoint — should return 200 + a JSON welcome
GET {{host}}/api/hello
Accept: application/json
# curl equivalent:
#   curl -i http://localhost:8080/api/hello

### Liveness/readiness — should return {"status":"UP"}
GET {{host}}/actuator/health
Accept: application/json
# curl equivalent:
#   curl -s http://localhost:8080/actuator/health

### App info (build/step metadata)
GET {{host}}/actuator/info
Accept: application/json
